messages.message:
The spacing changes wont likely affect much between with and without table digitisation (table digitisation essentially uses FR).
First snapshot is without table detection digitize *And* second one is with table detection digitize.
The actual text that LLM sees with enabling table detection is a markdown enriched text (with table markdown, checkbox , paragraph odering etc) - so that might be affecting this - sample of that view is also attached (last snapshot).
We have observed this in last few weeks as build team was zeroing down on improving build extraction accuracy on form kind of docs. So we will need those changes to be implemented to help here. cc: @lydia
Also that apart are we primarily using table detection here for detecting checkboxes ?
wonder if it would be possible to explore using different digitization profiles for different fields/classes :thinking_face:
